Title: Calder Shank Nail annular ring shank nails 1kg 30mm Copper (1kg bag)
Description: Made of copper, these Calder 30mm length, 3.35mm diameter shank nails are specifically designed and manufactured to meet the requirements of British Standard BS 1202-1 and 2. This standard stipulates that nails intended for light duty use should have a minimum shank diameter of 2.65mm and for heavy duty use nails should have a shank diameter of at least 3.35mm.
